                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">If that applies to trade union leaders, does it not also apply to employers?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a10e8170-4ad5-4d6b-bd53-5b62d63c28d0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-09-19/debates/c848e441-7fb9-4b7e-918d-bc202ac6abd5/IronAndSteelNationalisation#contribution-a10e8170-4ad5-4d6b-bd53-5b62d63c28d0">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
