                Mr. Morrison
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ba147c41-8ca5-441d-b6ab-5031ebf3c0ae" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-09-19/debates/c848e441-7fb9-4b7e-918d-bc202ac6abd5/IronAndSteelNationalisation#contribution-ba147c41-8ca5-441d-b6ab-5031ebf3c0ae">
