    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Would the hon. Member be good enough to agree again that there is some reason why it is impossible for the new Corporation to put into operation the known best practices of the existing system?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-a97e87d9-2080-4c5a-a7d2-004830075d7c" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-09-19/debates/c848e441-7fb9-4b7e-918d-bc202ac6abd5/IronAndSteelNationalisation#contribution-a97e87d9-2080-4c5a-a7d2-004830075d7c">
