<p class="">The Government's Economic Survey, published this year, stated that owing to the export of electrical generating machinery <span id="1783" class="column-number" data-column-number="1783"></span> there will be a shortage for many years, both for industry and for domestic users.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e2f62570-e156-4693-859d-f212cfd8ebab" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
