<p class="">The vast mass of the people, the overwhelming majority of the people in the road transport industry—I am speaking of road transport—did not want their industry nationalised, and they do not want it nationalised now.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
