        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-9d8ae566-3104-485b-83b9-0c3ca711594a">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-9d8ae566-3104-485b-83b9-0c3ca711594a">
                Mr. Osborne
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9d8ae566-3104-485b-83b9-0c3ca711594a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1950-09-19/debates/c848e441-7fb9-4b7e-918d-bc202ac6abd5/IronAndSteelNationalisation#contribution-9d8ae566-3104-485b-83b9-0c3ca711594a">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">What about devaluation? Did the Government keep their word then?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
